<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 6rem;
            margin: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out 0.5s forwards;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out 1s forwards;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .floating-books {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 3rem;
            opacity: 0.2;
            animation: float 5s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
        }
        .book1 { top: 10%; left: 20%; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .book2 { top: 30%; left: 70%; animation-delay: 1s; }
        .book3 { top: 60%; left: 40%; animation-delay: 2s; }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes float {
            from { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: translateY(-15px) rotate(5deg); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>404</h1>
    <h4>Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.</h4>
    <h4>Maybe it's lost in the world of words...</h4>
    <a href="/">Back to Home</a>
    
